@cosmopolitan readers selected not one but three Drunk Elephant products as winners of the Cosmopolitan Readers’ Choice Beauty Awards for 2024!
 
⭐️ Protini Cream: Best Wrinkle Cream
⭐️ Virgin Marula Oil: Best Face Oil
⭐️ D-Bronzi: Best Makeup Game Changer
 
Thank you to everyone who voted, plus beauty editor @ebethgillette and beauty director @laurenbalsamo. Read the full feature via link in our bio.
